  {
    "client_msg_id": "eb861d95-b231-4a21-8e0c-9328af823ef1",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Not only don't I care about performance, I think the obsession with performance is itself a big part of the problem with programming. Performance is the sort of crisp quantifiable puzzle nerds love to work on, unlike the messy subjective problems of making things simpler and easier.",
